OL,5, Water customers in England and Wales   
OL,6, may be owed #163m for sewage spills,   
OL,7, corporate wrongdoing researchers claim.
OL,9,FWater firms charge customers to treat  
OL,10,Fsewage, but instead have been widely   
OL,11,Fdischarging it in to rivers and on to  
OL,12,Fbeaches, researchers from Fideres said.
OL,14,FThe firms have not invested enough,    
OL,15,Fleading to an "excessively low quality 
OL,16,Fservice", the researchers said.        
OL,18,FHowever, a water industry body said    
OL,19,Ffirms were putting in place a #56bn    
OL,20,Fprogramme to tackle spills.            
